<item>
            <title>[CXF-3024] Response.temporaryRedirect() cannot handle query parameter correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3024</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider the following code that wants to redirect to a non-absolute URL containing query parameters:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; cssLink1=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//yui.yahooapis.com/3.2.0/build/cssreset/reset-min.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; Response.temporaryRedirect(UriBuilder.fromPath(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;whatever/redirection&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).queryParam(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;css1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,cssLink1).build()).build();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The created Location header of the response will contain the following value:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://myserver/app/services/public/whatever/redirection%3Fcss1=http:/yui.yahooapis.com/3.2.0/build/cssreset/reset-min.css&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://myserver/app/services/public/whatever/redirection%3Fcss1=http:/yui.yahooapis.com/3.2.0/build/cssreset/reset-min.css&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;IMHO this should be:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://myserver/app/services/public/whatever/redirection?css1=http:/yui.yahooapis.com/3.2.0/build/cssreset/reset-min.css&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://myserver/app/services/public/whatever/redirection?css1=http:/yui.yahooapis.com/3.2.0/build/cssreset/reset-min.css&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
