                            <comment id="12918082" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Tue, 5 Oct 2010 17:30:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this is fixed now, thanks.&lt;br/&gt;
Workaround for 2.2.10 :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;@Context UriInfo ui;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;return Response.status(307).header(&quot;Location&quot;, ui.getBaseUriBuilder().path(&quot;/some/path&quot;).queryParam(&quot;css&quot;, &quot;http://...&quot;).build()).build()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cheers, Sergey&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
